le=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uia1665702644018.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uia1665702644018.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uia1665702644018.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uia1665702644018\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Image Type\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Type of image to use as a background or icon—<code class=\"ph codeph\">Glyph</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">File</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uia1665702644018__section_w216ab1b5b1_w217ab1b5_w218ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">(None)</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__2\">\n No image is used\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Glyph</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__2\">\n Use the specified glyph.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">File</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12377e1_d12378e1_d12379e1__entry__2\">\n Use the specified file.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uia1665702644018__section_uqm_ygf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d864665e130\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"uia1665702644018__table_d12380e1_d12381e1_d12382e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Image File</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Background\n                              Image</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uia1665702644018__section_dmz_zgf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d864665e200\">Map Widget</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uia1665702644018__p_d104792e1_d104793e1_d104794e1\">For map widgets, this property defines the type of\n            image to use as the background image on the map widget. The default is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Glyph</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uia1665702644018__p_d104795e1_d104796e1_d104797e1\">Specify the image to use in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Image\n               Name</span> property.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uia1665702644018__section_un3_bhf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d864665e218\">Application Shell, Form, and Default Entity Widget</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uia1665702644018__p_d104801e1_d104802e1_d104803e1\">For application shells, forms, and entities, this\n            property defines the type of image to use as a background image. Uniface automatically\n            resizes the image to fit the window (subject to the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Preserve Aspect\n               Ratio</span> property).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uia1665702644018__p_d104804e1_d104805e1_d104806e1\">Specify the image to use in the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Background Image</span> property.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uia1665702644018__section_ad5_2hf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d864665e236\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"uia1665702644018__ul_mrk_fhf_ywb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uia1665702644018__li_d41831e1_d41832e1_d41833e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gls1665702643795.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gls1665702643795.html\" title=\"The umap widget defines areas on an image that allow the user to interact by clicking on that area. It can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called Map, which is mapped to umap.\">umap (Map)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uia1665702644018__li_d41834e1_d41835e1_d41836e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ohj1705472401504.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ohj1705472401504.html\" title=\"An application shell is a module used to initialize and run an application (Windows or character-based) or application server.\">Application Shells</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uia1665702644018__li_d41837e1_d41838e1_d41839e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"usl1704692305727.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/usl1704692305727.html\" title=\"Form components provide the user interface for Uniface desktop applications. They are always executed on the client system and can be modal (form retains focus until it is closed) or non-modal (users can switch focus to other forms).\">Forms</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uia1665702644018__li_d41840e1_d41841e1_d41842e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ula1665702613468.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ula1665702613468.html\" title=\"An Entity defines a logical data aggregation. It usually represents a relational database table, but it is possible to define non-database entities for transient data, reusable user interface controls, or other application structures.\">Entities</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uia1665702644018__li_d41843e1_d41844e1_d41845e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ujj1665702610581.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ujj1665702610581.html\" title=\"Area frames are objects that can be used to group or separate the contents of a Form component.\">Area Frames and Lines</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616304\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616304\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Image Type Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Image Type Type of image to use as a background or icon— Glyph or File . Value Description (None) No image is used Glyph Use the specified glyph. File Use the specified file. Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Image File or Background Image Map Widget For map widgets, this property defines the type of image to use as the background image on the map widget. The default is Glyph . Specify the image to use in the Image Name property. Application Shell, Form, and Default Entity Widget For application shells, forms, and entities, this property defines the type of image to use as a background image. Uniface automatically resizes the image to fit the window (subject to the Preserve Aspect Ratio property). Specify the image to use in the Background Image property. Applies to umap (Map) Application Shells Forms Entities Area Frames and Lines Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}